4. Backend will run at `http://localhost:5000`

### Frontend

1. Open `frontend/index.html` in your browser.
2. Chat away!

---

## Features

- Chat interface with user and AI messages
- Voice input button (if browser supports speech recognition)
- Simple AI reply simulation on backend

